{# THE GARDEN - How Ferni Stays Free #}
<section class="section garden" id="garden">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Community-Funded</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">How Ferni stays free</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="garden__content">
      <div class="garden__intro">
        <p class="garden__lead">
          Most AI companies charge $20-50/month. We asked: <em>what if we just... didn't?</em>
        </p>
        <p class="garden__text">
          Ferni doesn't have investors demanding growth. It has a community planting seeds. When people who can afford to give a little do, everyone benefits.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="garden__model">
        <div class="garden__pillar">
          <div class="garden__pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M7 20h10"/><path d="M10 20c5.5-2.5.8-6.4 3-10"/><path d="M9.5 9.4c1.1.8 1.8 2.2 2.3 3.7-2 .4-3.5.4-4.8-.3-1.2-.6-2.3-1.9-3-4.2 2.8-.5 4.4 0 5.5.8z"/><path d="M14.1 6a7 7 0 0 0-1.1 4c1.9-.1 3.3-.6 4.3-1.4 1-1 1.6-2.3 1.7-4.6-2.7.1-4 1-4.9 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="garden__pillar-title">Seeds, Not Subscriptions</h3>
          <p class="garden__pillar-desc">Contributions are called "seeds." You're not paying for a service—you're nurturing a community.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="garden__pillar">
          <div class="garden__pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="32" height="32">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v8"/><path d="M8 12h8"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="garden__pillar-title">No Paywalls. Ever.</h3>
          <p class="garden__pillar-desc">You'll never hit a paywall when you need support most. The garden keeps Ferni free for everyone.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="garden__pillar">
          <div class="garden__pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="garden__pillar-title">Gardeners, Not Customers</h3>
          <p class="garden__pillar-desc">Contributors are gardeners tending to something alive. Free users tend the garden too—by showing up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="garden__cta">
        <p class="garden__promise">When enough people give a little, everyone gets a lot.</p>
        <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}?garden=true" class="btn btn--garden">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="18" height="18">
            <path d="M7 20h10"/><path d="M10 20c5.5-2.5.8-6.4 3-10"/><path d="M9.5 9.4c1.1.8 1.8 2.2 2.3 3.7-2 .4-3.5.4-4.8-.3-1.2-.6-2.3-1.9-3-4.2 2.8-.5 4.4 0 5.5.8z"/><path d="M14.1 6a7 7 0 0 0-1.1 4c1.9-.1 3.3-.6 4.3-1.4 1-1 1.6-2.3 1.7-4.6-2.7.1-4 1-4.9 2z"/>
          </svg>
          Plant a Seed
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

