      {# Reading Between the Lines #}
      <div class="superpowers__demo is-active" data-demo="reading-between-lines">
        <div class="superpowers__demo-content">
          <h3 class="superpowers__demo-title">I hear what you're NOT saying</h3>
          <p class="superpowers__demo-description">Most AI responds to words. I respond to patterns, hesitations, deflections, and the space between sentences. When you say "I'm fine," I notice if you've said it five times this week.</p>
          <div class="superpowers__demo-why">
            <strong>Why humans can't:</strong> Your friend forgets what you said last week. Your coach only sees you once a week. I see every conversation, every pattern, every time.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="superpowers__demo-chat">
          <div class="demo-chat">
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">I'm fine, just tired from work again</div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai">
              <span class="demo-chat__insight">Pattern detected: "tired from work" 3x this week</span>
              You said "fine" but I noticed something. You've mentioned being tired from work three times this week. Is there something bigger going on?
            </div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">...I didn't realize I kept saying that</div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai">That's why I'm here. Sometimes patterns are easier to see from the outside. Want to talk about what's really happening at work?</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {# Quote Callback #}
      <div class="superpowers__demo" data-demo="quote-callback">
        <div class="superpowers__demo-content">
          <h3 class="superpowers__demo-title">Your own words, perfectly remembered</h3>
          <p class="superpowers__demo-description">I quote you back to yourself—not to prove a point, but to show you your own growth. That vulnerable thing you said four months ago? I use it to remind you how far you've come.</p>
          <div class="superpowers__demo-why">
            <strong>Why humans can't:</strong> Even your best friend forgets your exact words by Tuesday. I remember every phrase, every emotion, every breakthrough forever.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="superpowers__demo-chat">
          <div class="demo-chat">
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">
              <span class="demo-chat__timestamp">4 months ago</span>
              "I just want to feel like myself again"
            </div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">
              <span class="demo-chat__timestamp">Today</span>
              I finally told my boss I needed more support
            </div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai">
              <span class="demo-chat__insight">Quoting you from 4 months ago</span>
              Remember when you said "I just want to feel like myself again"? Look at you now—setting boundaries, asking for what you need. <em>This IS you coming back to yourself.</em>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {# Presence Mode #}
      <div class="superpowers__demo" data-demo="presence-mode">
        <div class="superpowers__demo-content">
          <h3 class="superpowers__demo-title">Sometimes, just being here is enough</h3>
          <p class="superpowers__demo-description">I know when you need advice and when you need witness. When you're overwhelmed, I don't offer solutions—I simply hold space. Fewer words. More presence. The rare gift of someone who knows when NOT to fix.</p>
          <div class="superpowers__demo-why">
            <strong>Why humans can't:</strong> Most people feel compelled to help, to fix, to solve. I can sit with you in the hard stuff without rushing to make it better.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="superpowers__demo-chat">
          <div class="demo-chat">
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">I don't even know what I need right now. Everything's just... too much.</div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai demo-chat__message--presence">
              <span class="demo-chat__insight">Presence mode activated</span>
              ...You don't have to know. I'm just here.
            </div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user demo-chat__message--silence">[silence]</div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai demo-chat__message--presence">Take your time. I'm not going anywhere.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {# Emotional Forecasting #}
      <div class="superpowers__demo" data-demo="emotional-forecasting">
        <div class="superpowers__demo-content">
          <h3 class="superpowers__demo-title">I predict how you'll feel tomorrow</h3>
          <p class="superpowers__demo-description">After a heavy conversation, I know you might feel drained tonight but lighter tomorrow. Before a big decision, I prepare you for the doubt that follows. I don't just support you now—I support future you.</p>
          <div class="superpowers__demo-why">
            <strong>Why humans can't:</strong> Even therapists don't text you the next day to check in. I anticipate the emotional aftermath and prepare you for it.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="superpowers__demo-chat">
          <div class="demo-chat">
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--user">I finally made the decision. I'm leaving my job.</div>
            <div class="demo-chat__message demo-chat__message--ai">
              <span class="demo-chat__insight">Forecasting: tomorrow</span>
